---
import SharedPageLayout from "../components/SharedPageLayout.astro";
---

<SharedPageLayout title="Why Us | Done Deal Digital" bodyClass="bg-background-light font-dmsans text-navy">
    <Fragment slot="head">
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>

<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&amp;family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;700&amp;family=Work+Sans:wght@400;700&amp;family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script id="tailwind-config">
        tailwind.config = {
            darkMode: "class",
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        "primary": "#FF7B00", // Construction Orange
                        "navy": "#0B1D33",
                        "concrete": "#E2E8F0",
                        "background-light": "#f6f6f8",
                        "background-dark": "#0B1D33",
                        "grid-gray": "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05)"
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        "display": ["Work Sans", "sans-serif"],
                        "bebas": ["Bebas Neue", "cursive"],
                        "dmsans": ["DM Sans", "sans-serif"]
                    },
                    borderRadius: {
                        "none": "0",
                        "DEFAULT": "0",
                        "lg": "0",
                        "xl": "0",
                        "full": "9999px"
                    },
                    borderWidth: {
                        "3": "3px"
                    }
                },
            },
        }
    </script>
<style type="text/tailwindcss">
        @tailwind base;
        @tailwind components;
        @tailwind utilities;

        @layer utilities {
            .graph-paper {
                background-size: 40px 40px;
                background-image: 
                    linear-gradient(to right, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
                    linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
            }
            .block-shadow {
                box-shadow: 8px 8px 0px 0px rgba(11, 29, 51, 1);
            }
            .block-shadow-orange {
                box-shadow: 8px 8px 0px 0px #FF7B00;
            }
            .diagonal-stripes {
                background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03) 0, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03) 10px, transparent 10px, transparent 20px);
            }
            .bw-overlay {
                filter: grayscale(1) contrast(1.2);
            }
            .bebas-heavy {
                font-weight: 700;
                letter-spacing: 0.02em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</Fragment>

<section class="relative bg-navy overflow-hidden border-b-2 border-navy">
<div class="absolute inset-0 graph-paper opacity-40"></div>
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-20 py-32 relative z-10 text-center">
<div class="inline-block border-4 border-primary p-4 mb-8">
<span class="text-white font-bebas bebas-heavy text-2xl tracking-[.2em] uppercase">REAL PEOPLE. CLEAR PROCESS.</span>
</div>
<h1 class="font-bebas bebas-heavy text-7xl md:text-9xl text-white leading-[0.85] uppercase mb-8">
                YOU'RE NOT HIRING A <br/><span class="text-primary">MYSTERY AGENCY.</span>
</h1>
<p class="text-concrete text-2xl md:text-3xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-medium">
                You’ll know who you’re working with, how we communicate, and what we’re responsible for.
            </p>
</div>
</section>
<section class="bg-white py-24 border-b-2 border-navy">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-20">
<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
<div class="border-4 border-navy p-12 block-shadow">
<h2 class="font-bebas bebas-heavy text-6xl text-navy mb-8">WHY DONE DEAL DIGITAL EXISTS</h2>
<p class="text-xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 font-medium">
                        Most agencies speak in agency language. We built this firm so local service businesses can get practical, direct recommendations.
                    </p>
<p class="text-xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                        We focus on outcomes owners can verify: clearer contact flow, better messaging, and cleaner systems.
                    </p>
</div>
<div class="space-y-8">
<div class="flex gap-6 items-center border-l-8 border-primary pl-8 py-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl text-navy">verified_user</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-bebas text-3xl text-navy">WE SHOW UP</h4>
<p class="font-medium text-slate-600 uppercase text-sm tracking-widest">No ghosting. We keep promises and schedules.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-6 items-center border-l-8 border-navy pl-8 py-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl text-navy">visibility</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-bebas text-3xl text-navy">CLEAR SCOPE</h4>
<p class="font-medium text-slate-600 uppercase text-sm tracking-widest">No hidden work. Everything is documented.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-6 items-center border-l-8 border-primary pl-8 py-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl text-navy">speed</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-bebas text-3xl text-navy">SPEAK THE TRUTH EARLY</h4>
<p class="font-medium text-slate-600 uppercase text-sm tracking-widest">We tell you if the fit is weak before we begin.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="bg-background-light py-24 border-b-2 border-navy">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-20">
<h2 class="font-bebas bebas-heavy text-6xl text-navy mb-16 text-center">MEET THE FOUNDERS</h2>
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
<div class="bg-white border-2 border-navy block-shadow">
<div class="h-[400px] border-b-2 border-navy relative overflow-hidden">
<img alt="Travis - Founder" class="w-full h-full object-cover bw-overlay" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCQuKBUbvbDTfbjUT2ZSf2ttnd_NQ_Bnzh4GTmGjrQ_vjNFFmWfjNqvpxdtIgurxkO41Ms1uAIYKk90rC1Vg8wZ-Vk7hJTuy_n0KNBrtOgyEGvaCHAftAD4GLhzK1_HprKZVjxGAs73lhzWP46pgIY5G0_fjckrc2j0hnSSd5f0RQGEqnmrRgVcT8EL_i1raG-Su5xOM4HCjjToRVmSBmG5gyxxSZRXcQqCYz5g6HM7x8rl8InYWQDLRfxBG6B-cQN9rC6HFJfyeBo"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-navy/20 mix-blend-multiply"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 bg-primary text-white px-4 py-2 border-2 border-navy">
<span class="font-bebas text-2xl tracking-widest">TRAVIS</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="p-8">
<h4 class="font-bebas text-3xl mb-2 text-navy">THE STRATEGIST</h4>
<p class="text-slate-600 font-medium mb-6">Former field operator with direct service business experience. Travis handles offer positioning and owner-facing planning.</p>
<div class="flex gap-2 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-navy bg-concrete p-3 border border-navy/10">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">precision_manufacturing</span> FIELD EXPERIENCE + OPERATIONS
                        </div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="bg-white border-2 border-navy block-shadow-orange">
<div class="h-[400px] border-b-2 border-navy relative overflow-hidden">
<img alt="Jacob - Founder" class="w-full h-full object-cover bw-overlay" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAp_gOZtrpGI8YFT12b7cezFByoLUrfqkjMp1MqjubNpzt7Fj_47ZKM-ju99RBfjdjSM83wzjvky4mRDEXxX9OXadl1ubIQLe9tFoI-fLMq5PhWpT7XYHhaKhsSqdaxhOpPDH7zZAsijxv_HiVqZRThBpChlmSSAX-Ge947hOrtz5U7AsVpkRToDvF-cNxE6kgpY88ZPP99ygXjrccU6zkhUF7NdPUF1Q-_M-fCsoLr5P1BUAH76YtsqX5XqtcKeUJSA0wT28J9iqo"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/20 mix-blend-multiply"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 bg-navy text-white px-4 py-2 border-2 border-white">
<span class="font-bebas text-2xl tracking-widest">JACOB</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="p-8">
<h4 class="font-bebas text-3xl mb-2 text-navy">THE ARCHITECT</h4>
<p class="text-slate-600 font-medium mb-6">Digital execution specialist. Jacob keeps builds fast, stable, and easier for owners and teams to use.</p>
<div class="flex gap-2 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-navy bg-concrete p-3 border border-navy/10">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">code</span> WEB PERFORMANCE + DELIVERY
                        </div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="bg-concrete py-24 border-b-2 border-navy relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 diagonal-stripes"></div>
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-20 relative z-10 text-center">
<h2 class="font-bebas bebas-heavy text-7xl text-navy mb-8">WHY SERVICE BUSINESSES?</h2>
<p class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-tight italic">
                "Service businesses need a partner that shows up, does what it says, and follows through."
            </p>
<div class="mt-12 flex justify-center gap-4">
<div class="w-16 h-2 bg-primary"></div>
<div class="w-16 h-2 bg-navy"></div>
<div class="w-16 h-2 bg-primary"></div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="py-24 bg-white border-b-2 border-navy">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-20">
<h2 class="font-bebas bebas-heavy text-6xl text-navy mb-16">PRINCIPLES</h2>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-5 gap-6">
<div class="border-2 border-navy p-8 bg-white block-shadow flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary mb-4">event_available</span>
<h4 class="font-bebas text-2xl text-navy mb-2">1. WE SHOW UP</h4>
<p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-slate-500 leading-tight">No ghosting. Ever.</p>
</div>
<div class="border-2 border-navy p-8 bg-white block-shadow flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary mb-4">assignment</span>
<h4 class="font-bebas text-2xl text-navy mb-2">2. CLEAR SCOPE</h4>
<p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-slate-500 leading-tight">Everything in writing.</p>
</div>
<div class="border-2 border-navy p-8 bg-white block-shadow flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary mb-4">gavel</span>
<h4 class="font-bebas text-2xl text-navy mb-2">3. HARD TRUTHS</h4>
<p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-slate-500 leading-tight">No sugar coating early.</p>
</div>
<div class="border-2 border-navy p-8 bg-white block-shadow flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary mb-4">settings_suggest</span>
<h4 class="font-bebas text-2xl text-navy mb-2">4. BUILT FOR USE</h4>
<p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-slate-500 leading-tight">Tools, not toys.</p>
</div>
<div class="border-2 border-navy p-8 bg-white block-shadow flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary mb-4">support_agent</span>
<h4 class="font-bebas text-2xl text-navy mb-2">5. POST-LAUNCH</h4>
<p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-slate-500 leading-tight">Support after launch.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="py-24 bg-navy text-white border-b-2 border-navy">
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
<h2 class="font-bebas bebas-heavy text-6xl text-white mb-12 text-center underline decoration-primary underline-offset-8">WHAT WORKING WITH US FEELS LIKE</h2>
<div class="space-y-4">
<div class="border-2 border-white/20 p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center bg-white/5">
<div class="text-primary font-bebas text-4xl italic">COMMUNICATION</div>
<div class="text-lg text-concrete font-medium border-l-2 border-primary/30 pl-8">
                        Direct access to the team. Clear ownership and concise updates.
                    </div>
</div>
<div class="border-2 border-white/20 p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center bg-white/5">
<div class="text-primary font-bebas text-4xl italic">RESPONSE TIMES</div>
<div class="text-lg text-concrete font-medium border-l-2 border-primary/30 pl-8">
                        Emergency issues handled same-day. General requests within 24 business hours.
                    </div>
</div>
<div class="border-2 border-white/20 p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center bg-white/5">
<div class="text-primary font-bebas text-4xl italic">REVISIONS</div>
<div class="text-lg text-concrete font-medium border-l-2 border-primary/30 pl-8">
                        One structured revision pass is included, with adjustments focused on the agreed goals.
                    </div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="py-24 bg-white">
<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
<div class="border-4 border-navy p-16 relative bg-white block-shadow">
<div class="absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-primary px-8 py-3 border-2 border-navy">
<span class="text-white font-bebas bebas-heavy text-2xl uppercase tracking-widest">READY TO WORK?</span>
</div>
<div class="text-center">
<h2 class="font-bebas bebas-heavy text-7xl text-navy mb-8">READY TO WORK WITH PEOPLE WHO FOLLOW THROUGH?</h2>
<p class="text-2xl text-slate-600 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium">If you're tired of unclear ownership and ready for a straightforward process, let's have a conversation.</p>
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-8">
<button class="bg-primary hover:bg-orange-600 text-white px-16 py-6 font-bold text-3xl uppercase tracking-widest border-2 border-navy block-shadow-orange w-full md:w-auto">
                            LET'S TALK
                        </button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

</SharedPageLayout>
